<!-- /sections/section-feature-enterprise-grade-security.liquid -->

<div id="section-feature-enterprise-grade-security" class="section-row {{ section.settings.color_bg }}" 
  style="--PT: {{ section.settings.padding_top }}px; --PB: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px;">
  <div class="{{ section.settings.width }} section-padding">

    
    <div class="text__standard" style="margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <h1 class="h2 standard__heading heading-size-6" >Enterprise grade Security</h1>
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" >
        <p>Enterprise-grade Cybersecurity that keeps your online data safe and protects all your devices</p>
        <p>Deeper Connect's enterprise-grade cybersecurity comes with a 7-layer firewall and deep packet inspection that protects your entire family from viruses, Trojans, tracking, and other malicious activities.</p>
      </div>
    <div>

      <div style="background-color:#F7F7FB;padding-bottom:20px; margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px; display: flex; flex-direction: row;justify-content: space-around; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <div class="one-quarter mobile--one-whole ppImage">
          <img
                loading="lazy" 
                width="100%"
                src="{{ 'fegs-001.png' | asset_url }}"                
                sizes="(min-width: 768px), 90vw, 100vw"/>
        </div>
        <div class="one-quarter mobile--one-whole ppImage">
          <img
                loading="lazy" 
                width="100%"
                src="{{ 'fegs-002.png' | asset_url }}"                
                sizes="(min-width: 768px), 90vw, 100vw"/>
        </div>
        <div class="one-quarter mobile--one-whole ppImage">
          <img
                loading="lazy"  
                width="100%"
                src="{{ 'fegs-003.png' | asset_url }}"                
                sizes="(min-width: 768px), 90vw, 100vw"/>
        </div>
        <div class="one-quarter mobile--one-whole ppImage">
          <img
                loading="lazy"  
                width="100%"
                src="{{ 'fegs-004.png' | asset_url }}"                
                sizes="(min-width: 768px), 90vw, 100vw"/>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text__standard" style="margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <div class="standard__rte body-size-2" >
        <p>Deeper Connect comes with a fully featured suite of enterprise-grade security functions to keep you safe while online and protect your IoT devices. Never again worry about you and your familyâ€™s safety while browsing online and rest easy knowing that every device in your network is secure.</p>
        <p>AtomOS, the lock-free operating system running on the Deeper Connect, provides a 7-layer firewall with deep packet inspection, anti-tracking, intrusion prevention and more. These features are typically only found in enterprise-grade cybersecurity products that costs several times more than the Deeper Connect.</p>
        <p>There is no configuration necessary. Simply power the device on and have peace of mind knowing that your personal information, IoT devices, and anything connected on your network is fully protected by our suite of cybersecurity features. </p>
      </div>
    <div>

    <div class="overlap" style="margin-bottom: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom }}px">
      <div class="overlap__item overlap__image">
        <img src="{{ 'fegs-comparision.png' | asset_url }}" />
      </div>
    </div>
 

    

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  #section-feature-enterprise-grade-security .text__standard{
    color: #170F49 !important;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
</style>

